&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:63t7Ie-LG7Y"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=63t7Ie-LG7Y" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:-BTjWOF_DHI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?i=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:dnMXMwOfBR0"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=dnMXMwOfBR0" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:F7zBnMyn0Lo"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?i=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:7Q72WNTAKBA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=7Q72WNTAKBA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:V_sGLiPBpWU"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?i=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:qj6IDK7rITs"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:KwTdNBX3Jqk"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?i=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:KwTdNBX3Jqk" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:l6gmwiTKsz0"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=l6gmwiTKsz0" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:gIN9vFwOqvQ"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?i=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?a=5M1SR-rbJ14:ThacXgGXK8g:TzevzKxY174"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/blogspot/ipXWW?d=TzevzKxY174" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/blogspot/ipXWW/~4/5M1SR-rbJ14" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/blogspot/ipXWW/~3/5M1SR-rbJ14/jobstickers-podcast-4-sample-interview.html</link><author>warzel@mjwcareers.com (Matt Warzel)</author><thr:total>0</thr:total><enclosure url="http://www.clevelandclowns.com/podcasts/021411.mp3" length="12813083" type="audio/mpeg" /><media:content url="http://www.clevelandclowns.com/podcasts/021411.mp3" fileSize="12813083" type="audio/mpeg" /><itunes:explicit>no</itunes:explicit><itunes:subtitle>LISTEN: For the 4th installment of the MJW Careers' JobSticker's podcast, we will be discussing some sample interview closing questions. You should always be asking questions at the end of an interview! On the show, we discussed some tips and don't forget</itunes:subtitle><itunes:author>Matt Warzel</itunes:author><itunes:summary>LISTEN: For the 4th installment of the MJW Careers' JobSticker's podcast, we will be discussing some sample interview closing questions. You should always be asking questions at the end of an interview! On the show, we discussed some tips and don't forget about our Free Resume contest. For more info about these and other great job hunting tips, please visit www.jobstickers.com or our website www.mjwcareers.com. For more information on the "Free Resume" contest, check out http://mjwcareers.blogspot.com/2011/01/announcing-free-resume-contest.html</itunes:summary><itunes:keywords>career,podcast,job,employment,tips,techniques,interview,resume,search,networking,marketing,counseling,loss,mjw,careers,matt,warzel</itunes:keywords><feedburner:origLink>http://mjwcareers.blogspot.com/2011/02/jobstickers-podcast-4-sample-interview.html</feedburner:origLink></item><item><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-6227544905063160909.post-128692158945965181</guid><pubDate>Tue, 08 Feb 2011 23:14:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2011-02-08T15:21:42.727-08:00</atom:update